SERVO - May 2010

SERVO Magazine is dedicated to the Next Generation of Robotics Experimenters, devoted 100% to robots and robotics. With an all robots - all the time focus, each monthly issue will inspire, educate, and entertain with feature articles, interviews, tutorials, DIY projects, hacks, parts sources and much more.
